## 2. System Architecture

### Three-Tier Architecture

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     CLIENT TIER                          │
│              React 19 + Vite 7 + TailwindCSS 4           │
│         Framer Motion • Recharts • Socket.io-client      │
│                     Port 5173                            │
└────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────┘
                         │ HTTP REST + WebSocket
┌────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┐
│                  APPLICATION TIER                        │
│        Express.js 4 + Prisma ORM + Socket.io             │
│     JWT Auth • Rate Limiting • express-validator          │
│                     Port 3000                            │
└────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────┘
                         │ HTTP REST (internal)
┌────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┐
│                  AI / COMPUTE TIER                       │
│           Python FastAPI + Playwright + axe-core          │
│      Multi-Agent Pipeline (Crawler → Tester → Reporter)  │
│                     Port 8000                            │
└────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
┌────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┐
│                  DATA / STORAGE TIER                     │
│         PostgreSQL 16 │ Redis 7 │ Neo4j 5 Community      │
│         Port 5432     │ Port 6379 │ Port 7474/7687       │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Service Communication Matrix

| From → To | Protocol | Purpose |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| Frontend → Gateway | HTTP REST | Auth, CRUD, test initiation |
| Frontend → Gateway | WebSocket (Socket.io) | Real-time test progress updates |
| Gateway → AI Core | HTTP REST (internal) | Trigger test runs, cancel tests |
| AI Core → Gateway | HTTP REST (callback) | Incremental progress reporting |
| Gateway → PostgreSQL | Prisma ORM (TCP) | Persistent data storage |
| AI Core → Target Web App | Playwright (Chromium) | Crawling & testing target URLs |

